results.question: What impact will this new policy have on consumers and the global market?
results.answer: This 100% tax will cause price increases for customers, create adverse effects in international trade, and create uncertainty in the global market.

results.question: when did donald trump announce tarrifs
results.answer: Donald Trump announced the tariffs on August 6, 2025.

results.question: on which countries goods were taxes imposed
results.answer: A 100% duty has been imposed on the import of computer chips and other components from foreign countries (distribution‑distribution).
